<br>
i've always thought the idea of recoil was a cool one.  although i'm not sure it should be static.  i think it would be cool if we had a spell (especially something like SoM) that had a random chance to do the damage back to us instead of the target, maybe for a bigger payoff (ie trade high resist rate for a 2-5% chance of dealing the damage to yourself)  this would leave in the the random nature of the spell and maybe add a little variety to the way things are done. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=492380" target="top"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://filebox.vt.edu/users/jomarti8/signature.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=necridious>Necridious</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 370<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/25/03 3:50 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re</span><hr size=1> 2 things:<br>
<br>
1. Enchanters do enchant weapons-- Ever seen a Chanter pet?  This probably fulfills the promise in VI's eyes.  In addition, Enchanters already own 2 of the most important grouping roles in the game- Slow and Mez... and in addition have a cheap DS, and a lock on the single most important buff in the game- Clarity, as well as a lock on Haste.<br>
<br>
2.  I don't know how anything could possibly meet all the rules.  I see Wizards as being balanced with a slight upgrade to all nukes below 50--say 10%, and Post 50 but Pre 60 being fine if they move some big damage like sunstrike down lower--preferably 53 and 56, and post 60 with the addition of a Icebolt spell with the exact same stats as the mage's firebolt+10%, off a vendor at 61. <p><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=448514">Antrygus Windrose </a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=faramir42>Faramir42</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 135<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/26/03 7:14 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re</span><hr size=1> Actually, the spell weapon enchantment would be perfect. I posted on a different thread a similar idea. And while yes, it does seem like an enchanter spell, there is president.<br>
<br>
Call of the Hero, while teleporting is given to magicians under the idea they are summoning the person, not teleporting. Spell haste went to clerics, because the idea is the blessing clears your mind to cast spells faster.<br>
<br>
So, call it Ingnite Weapon, or Enflame Weapon or whatever, it doesn't have to be Enchant Weapon. It raises the weapons damage, lowers the delay and adds a damage bonus of Fire, magic or cold. It only effects the primary weapon, lasts, oh, say, 2 minutes at best, and is level based.<br>
<br>
I like the idea of a delayed Nuke. One that doesn't do it's damage right up, but later.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=799.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showPrevMessage?topicID=799.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showNextMessage?topicID=799.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.emailToFriend?topicID=799.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.threadControl?topicID=799.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=799.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=799.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub140.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding=